<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أح ن:</span> <span class="c2">(الْإِحْنَةُ)</span> الْحِقْدُ وَجَمْعُهَا <span class="c2">(إِحَنٌ)</span> وَلَا تَقُلْ: حِنَةٌ، وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(أَحِنَ)</span> عَلَيْهِ بِالْكَسْرِ يَأْحَنُ إِحْنَةً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
